cacheTempView(sql="
SELECT
  DISTINCT atb.orderDate,
  atb.utmContent,
  atb.orderId,
  atb.subOrderId,
  ftu.guid,
  ag.shippedStatus,
  ag.statusCode,
  atb.deviceType,
  ue.NMIncAd
FROM(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT orderDate,
      orderId,
      subOrderId,
      deviceType,
      utmContent
    FROM
      `temp.attributedOrders`
    WHERE
      (
        orderDate in ('2023-05-26','2023-05-27','2023-05-28','2023-05-29','2023-05-30','2023-05-31','2023-06-01','2023-06-02')
      )
      AND lower(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%plfeed%'
      AND lower(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%testns1%'
  ) atb
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT guid,
      orderId
    FROM
      `temp.shippedFTUs`
  ) ftu ON atb.orderId = ftu.orderId
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT subOrderId,
      shippedStatus,
      statusCode
    FROM
      `all(agCmDump)`
  ) ag ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT subOrderId,
      NMIncAd
    FROM
      `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
  ) ue ON atb.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId

","temp.content_rawData_1")

run(sql="
SELECT CASE WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d1%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D1V_ROAS_FTU_APP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d2%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D2V_ROAS_FTU_APP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%never%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'NVD_ROAS_FTU_APP'

            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d1%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D1V_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d2%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D2V_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%never%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'NVD_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            ELSE NULL END AS Campaign
        ,orderDate
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT orderId) AS InternalOrders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT subOrderId) AS Suborders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT guid) AS FTUs
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN guid IS NOT NULL THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS ftuSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS shippedSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(statusCode) LIKE '%del%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS deliveredSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN UPPER(deviceType) LIKE 'APP' THEN orderId ELSE NULL END) AS appOrders
        ,SUM(NMIncAd) AS NMIncAd
FROM `temp.content_rawData_1`
    
GROUP BY CASE WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d1%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D1V_ROAS_FTU_APP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d2%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D2V_ROAS_FTU_APP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%never%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%app%' THEN 'NVD_ROAS_FTU_APP'

            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d1%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D1V_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d2%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'D2V_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            WHEN LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%ftu%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%roas%'
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%never%' 
                    AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%app%' THEN 'NVD_ROAS_FTU_WAP'
            
            ELSE NULL END
        ,orderDate
ORDER BY Campaign ASC
        ,orderDate ASC
",1000)
